<br>
Mages will have to do chain research to get all their pets past 20th level.  There is always one pet available at a vendor, but the other three generallly require research.  <br>
<br>
Getting your research skill up takes a lot of combines and some of the components are hard find.  When it came time to do spell combines, I just used my training points to max my skill levels.  I then did my spell combines.  It cost pp at the trainer to get the levels, but it saves componets and you get your spells right away.  After I hit 49th level and got my last spell which required research, I went back and but 1 training point in all skills that were zero.  {Mostly language skills and trade skills}  I am banking the rest, for what I am not sure.    <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showPrevMessage?topicID=516.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showNextMessage?topicID=516.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=516.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.threadControl?topicID=516.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=516.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=516.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacin